The candidate gene i will be added to the module to build a new module by satisfying three criteria: (a) P(i) in Eq. (2) is less than 0.05 (connectivity significance), (b) this candidate gene is significantly co-expressed (P value < 0.05, F-statistic) within the neighborhood of the raw module based on RNA-seq profiles of tumor samples (see Methods section), and (c) \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
